Package fr.umlv.escape.move

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Movable
    Interface that all objects which can move should implements.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DownMove
    This class represent a down move.
    DownUpMove
    This class represent a down move followed by an up move.
    KamikazeMove
    This class represent a down move that follow the y position Player.
    LeftDampedMove
    This class represent a left move which is slowed until reaching a null velocity.
    LeftMove
    This class represent a left move.
    LeftRightMove
    This class represent a cycling left move followed by a right move.
    PlayerMove
    This class represent player move.
    RightDampedMove
    This class represent a Right move which is slowed until reaching a null velocity.
    RightMove
    This class represent a Right move.
    SquareLeft
    This class represent a square move.
    SquareRight
    This class represent a square move.
    StraightLine
    This class represent a straight line move.
    UpMove
    This class represent a up move.
    XRayMove
    This class represent the move of the XRay. it is just a left move accelerated.
